title: [Overgrown Trail]
description: A network of thin vines covers the oddly bent trees like some sort of shabby netting.  The trees grow closely together, intertwining with each other, slowly killing each other.  The tall grasses grow in regular clumps.  They sway in the moonlight as if in devout prayer.
